  "body": "Currently you can push a helm chart to an OCI registry in V3. \r\nWe need to support a unified way of storing credentials so that the user name and passwords can be used during push to an OCI registry. \r\n\r\nOutput of `helm version`:\r\nversion.BuildInfo{Version:\"v3.0+unreleased\", GitCommit:\"a32f8ebb377da054d21510671d63729fe6a00f3a\", GitTreeState:\"clean\"}\r\n\r\n/cc @jdolitsky @shizhMSFT\r\n\r\n\r\n",
